> >I don't have any other details except to say that EV's are great! My
> >electric Thing is saving me money while the price of gas goes up past
> >$1.70/gal. here in California. Fill the batteries every month with a
> >buck's worth of distilled water and $1.50 worth of Reddy Kilowatt and
> >I'm good for 30 miles a day.
>
>
